Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:48.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. Sensei's taking care\Nof my grandma right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:52.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, lots of weird stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:56.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:59.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a pretty inkstone.
