Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.07,0:02:24.03,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\be1}The White Which Lives Within the Ink Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:32.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei! Come, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei! Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:41.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:51.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier tonight, she started complaining that it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:55.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her friends next door are in the same condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her temperature's really low.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me another blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:07.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even her breath is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went into your shed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you touch anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, an inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inkstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:49.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, over here, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:02.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been careful not to let the villagers\Nsee the stuff in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:05.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm giving them hot water to keep them warm, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought it from a collector friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a beauty, of course, but apparently\Nit has the fossil of a Mushi in it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mushi fossil?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there even such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:31.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seldom leave any remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:36.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit buying stuff that you're not even sure of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:44.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that your passion is\Nof something of the paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a living Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what were the patients doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you do with the inkstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We grinded some ink...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just an inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's gotta be something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's water over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's try using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei's going to get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something cold just come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:45.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I inhaled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It regenerates by being used, enters\Nthe body and cools them inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to identify the Mushi with\Nonly that much to work from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:05:59.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't the former owner know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My friend says he doesn't know anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:12.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owners before that have all used it and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that remains is the craftsman that made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:21.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's got an inscription. We should\Nbe able to find the crafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:23.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:28.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:29.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:48.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quite a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:07:00.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, over there, but she's not\Nmaking any more inkstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She quit completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's got no relatives but she sure was talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is my inscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are people who are suffering\Nbecause of this inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was looking for this. For this inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:17.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, three people have used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard they all died within a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:30.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was some time after my inkstone\Ncraftsman father fell sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.99,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:41.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a client of my father's inkstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:49.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both he and his parents were against\Nme following my father's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tagane, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only my father and I can dig out the stones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to let it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't take on it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your workshop is getting less and less orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someday I'll make one as good as my father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,got to make something that he'll approve of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then... I threw myself into\Ninkstone crafting even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't make anything that I was happy with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one day, I dug up that stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strangely I was attracted to the stone,\Nand carved the stone intently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:53.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The finished inkstone was a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, try grinding on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:21.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some cloudy thing came out of the inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The texture is good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:48.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm confident that I can leave the workshop to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:01.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a few days since I inhaled\Nthat smoke, but I seem to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who saw it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he'd just reconsider on seeing this inkstone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I keep this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try to convince my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:27.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll send you a letter as soon as they're convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:34.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the letter I received a month later\Nwas one that notified me of his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:41.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since the day I gave him the inkstone\Nhe complained that it was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:46.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He became sick witih an illness that\Ncontinually reduced his body heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:52.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inkstone was accused of being sinister\Nand was sold off to a pawn shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:12:00.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I approached the shop, it was already sold,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I had no way of knowing where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:10.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just left with the rumors that came\Nfrom brokers and pawn shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:15.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Another one died using that inkstone."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:26.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father died shortly thereafter,\Nand I stopped making inkstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:32.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish I could be of help, but that's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, that was quite helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That inkstone... can I buy it off of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to destroy it with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come with me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:19.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't forget that your passion is\Nof something of the paranormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's really getting to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You better have something to be running your mouth–
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:36.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coal, stove...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, do you have a packboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mushi in the inkstone is called a "Kumohami".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a towering cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the name says, it consumes clouds –\Nthe ice and water particles in the air...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and makes it rain down snow and hail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:12.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then from the ground it looks as\Nif it's hailing without any clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's weak and immobile without wind, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:22.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When there's long periods without clouds it shrivels\Ndown and freezes itself into asphyxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:29.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inkstone must have just solidified into\Nstone, over tens of thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:37.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was brought back to the surface as an inkstone\Nand over time was revived with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what are we doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:47.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tagane-san, you said you passed a mountain\Nwhen you delivered the inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be why you weren't affected by the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're taking the patients to the\Ntallest mountain in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. Give her some warm water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:13.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll go ahead and boil some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:32.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, are we still going higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kids look painful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:41.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:48.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hold your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your face, you look...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not cold anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her body heat's returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Air pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:18.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That thing lives in the atmosphere where clouds do,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:22.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,meaning it must be of the same weight as the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd get sucked up if it got close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:27.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've always lived on high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smoke you've been inhaling must\Nhave gradually been fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:36.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must have gone away completely when you passed\Nover the mountain to deliver the inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake to allow such a dangerous\Nthing be subject to curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will take responsibility and see it destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know how to deal with it now, so it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:25.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you really say all the other stuff there is safe too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ginko, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:36.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To destroy the inkstone would mean to\Nkill the Mushi inside too, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.09,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the Mushi is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:48.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, that inkstone is too beautiful to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it like your own child to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:54.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:19:00.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's yourself that you can't forgive, for bringing\Nthat Mushi-bearing inkstone into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:07.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you free the Mushi from the inkstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, this is my inkstone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've a good bit of the responsibility,\NAdashino, for what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Face it, this is your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still a top notch inkstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:39.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:57.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gonna cost a fortune to fix all the roofs in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it takes me my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:06.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make inkstones again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to establish yourself soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I order one off you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll even take one with Mushi in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get over it, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:46.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll take me a while though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, when is it going to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since its last meal.
